data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled on the Houston National Golf Course! This 4B/3.5BA gem combines luxury & functionality. Versatile rooms provide spaces tailored to your lifestyle starting with the home office with dual access from the hall or entry. The formal dining room flows into the eat-in kitchen, complete with the cutest space for a coffee bar. Enjoy high ceilings & a fireplace in the living room. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bath, providing a private oasis for unwinding after a long day. Venture upstairs to discover a spacious game room & media room, designed for ultimate entertainment. A second primary bedroom with en-suite bath adds comfort for visitors. Step outside to the backyard, where the patio beckons you to enjoy breathtaking sunsets beyond the rolling green! Conveniently located near Hwy 290 & Hwy 6, this residence offers easy access to dining & shopping options. Don't miss the chance to make this exquisite property in the Stone Gate community your home!
